{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "e7c3b2a1-2222-4000-8000-ecommerce-dash-web",
		"name": "Ecommerce API ã Dashboard & Website",
		"description": "## Overview (English)\n\n### Folders\n- **Dashboard** ã Admin CRUD per resource (Mid-banners, Main-slider, Category-tiles, Products). Use `Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}` except **Auth**.\n- **Website** ã Storefront: **Auth** (full `/api/auth`), **Home** (aggregated home JSON), **Cart**, **Favorites** (wishlist).\n\n### Language query `?lang=`\nAppend **`?lang={{lang}}`** at the **end** of request URLs (collection variable `lang`: `en` or `ar`). Supported by server-side locale resolution for bilingual `message` fields on auth and shared error responses. Set `lang` in collection variables to switch.\n\n### Variables\n| Variable | Purpose |\n|----------|--------|\n| `baseUrl` | e.g. `http://localhost:8080` |\n| `lang` | `en` or `ar` ã appended as `?lang={{lang}}` on documented URLs |\n| `token` | User JWT (`ROLE_USER`) ã saved by Login (user) |\n| `adminToken` | Admin JWT ã saved by Login (admin) |\n| `productId`, `midBannerId`, `slideId`, `tileId` | Path segments for CRUD |\n\n### Cart (authenticated)\n| Method | Path | Body |\n|--------|------|------|\n| GET | `/api/web/cart?lang=ãÎ` | ã |\n| POST | `/api/web/cart/items?lang=ãÎ` | `{ \"productId\", \"quantity\" }` |\n| PUT | `/api/web/cart/items/{productId}?lang=ãÎ` | `{ \"quantity\" }` |\n| DELETE | `/api/web/cart/items/{productId}?lang=ãÎ` | ã |\n\n### Favorites / wishlist (authenticated)\n| Method | Path |\n|--------|------|\n| GET | `/api/web/favorites?lang=ãÎ` ã list saved products |\n| POST | `/api/web/favorites/{productId}?lang=ãÎ` ã add |\n| DELETE | `/api/web/favorites/{productId}?lang=ãÎ` ã remove |\n\n### Bootstrap admin\nSet `app.admin.email` and `app.admin.password` in `application.properties`, then start the app once.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{ "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
		{ "key": "lang", "value": "en" },
		{ "key": "token", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "adminToken", "value": "" },
		{ "key": "midBannerId", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "slideId", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "tileId", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "productId", "value": "1" },
		{ "key": "categoryId", "value": "1" }
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Dashboard",
			"description": "Admin panel ã full CRUD per folder. Header: `Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}`. Optional `?lang={{lang}}` on URLs for consistent locale in error payloads.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Auth",
					"description": "Login to populate `{{token}}` or `{{adminToken}}`.",
					"item": [
						{
							"name": "Login ã user (ROLE_USER)",
							"event": [
								{
									"listen": "test",
									"script": {
										"exec": [
											"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
											"  const j = pm.response.json();",
											"  if (j && j.token) pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", j.token);",
											"}"
										],
										"type": "text/javascript"
									}
								}
							],
							"request": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
								},
								"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login?lang={{lang}}"
							}
						},
						{
							"name": "Login ã admin (ROLE_ADMIN)",
							"event": [
								{
									"listen": "test",
									"script": {
										"exec": [
											"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
											"  const j = pm.response.json();",
											"  if (j && j.token) pm.collectionVariables.set(\"adminToken\", j.token);",
											"}"
										],
										"type": "text/javascript"
									}
								}
							],
							"request": {
								"method": "POST",
								"header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
								"body": {
									"mode": "raw",
									"raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@ecommerce.local\",\n  \"password\": \"ChangeMe123!\"\n}"
								},
								"url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login?lang={{lang}}",
								"description": "Uses `app.admin.email` and `app.admin.password` from `application.properties`."
							}
						}
					]
				},
